column2: How important is easy access to public transportation?
column3: How important is it for a neighborhood to be "driver-friendly"? (many major roads, parking available)
column4: How important is it for walking/biking to be a viable form of transportation in a neighborhood?
column5: How important is affordable housing in a neighborhood?
column6: How important is housing occupancy? (most homes occupied/not vacant)
column7: How important is long-term residency? (people tend to stay there for a longer period of time)
column8: How important is it for a neighborhood to be fairly drug-free? (low drug violations)
column9: How important is it for a neighborhood to have a low theft rate?
